It has a [[Gongen-zukuri]] style to its design<ref>{{Cite web |title=Kanasana-jinja {{!}} Honjo Sightseeing Association |url=https://en.honjo-kanko.jp/sightseeing/kanasana-jinja.html |access-date=2023-04-06 |website=en.honjo-kanko.jp}}</ref>

